Description: This package provides basic phylogenetic tree reconstruction algorithms for genomic or epigenomic data such as maximum likelihood, distance-based methods and parsimony. The library also allows to simulate sequence evolution based on evolutionary models and basic phylogenetic hypothesis testing.
